bio: Director of Exterior Design at Rivian | Photographer of Cars | Porsche 911 SC | SoCal

social_posts.post_text: One of my favorite parts of being at the track. Is watching the cars get warmed up and dialed in. You can almost hear the noise in the picture.

Just going to leave this one right here. Most people probably don’t even know what it is. But for me it defined a lot of my childhood. My mum had one( the very boring road version) when I was just a baby. Seeing these when I grew up a little older in rally and watching rally cross on Eurosport was life changing. Thank you @dirtfishrally for bringing it to @velocityinvitational
It’s all in the details. Lovely BMW 2002 livery!
Last set of this beauty // For now. 😎
One day I will own a racing Lotus // Velocity
Ladies and gentlemen @toddwilling beautiful Ford Escort. Period correct

Porsche Rennsport Reunion is Just around the corner. Excited to finally attend after years of watching through other people. Vintage racing is my passion closely followed by Porsche. Can’t wait. #childhooddreams #993cupcar #porsche
Who is ready for porsche wheel overload next week at Rennsport ?
Hope to see this again at Rennsport!
Should I shoot all black and white at Rennsport? Or too many cool liveries?
